{"tid":2336131,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2021年日本恢復旅遊！？預計2021年秋季後將正式開放日本旅遊","createTime":"2020-12-22T11:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T10:30:37.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e60ed20dd74c69a0845d622477faf75efcabfa","tid":2336131,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"12月3日《朝日新聞》上刊登了一篇令人鼓舞的文章。由於新冠病毒的傳播，入境遊客急劇減少， 2021年春季開始，日本政府開始考慮接受海外的小規模分散型旅遊，目的是恢復入境遊客（日本的外國觀光遊客）。首先將開始接受台灣等可以抑制新冠病毒感染的國家入境。預計將從少人數組成的小型旅遊團旅遊開始開放，疫情之前最受歡迎的自由行還未考慮開放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://yoshidakoichi.letsgojp.com/blog/1413/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoshidakoichi.letsgojp.com%2Fblog%2F1413%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=9db80eb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yoshidakoichi.letsgojp.com/blog/1413/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，連登仔要唔要？"},{"pid":"f9723370867393d31c9a35cd5bec56321beaf5f5","tid":2336131,"uid":117301,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:11:40.000Z","msg":"奧運點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffad2fcddf60e1191e053e48836b9415fb2e44c","tid":2336131,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9723370867393d31c9a35cd5bec56321beaf5f5","tid":2336131,"uid":117301,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:11:40.000Z","msg":"奧運點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:12:51.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"6e3e07e7f6b8cd694ec96aa0356d466e045c47c3","tid":2336131,"uid":60924,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"跟團不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i